          Critical Disclaimer
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl dark:text-gray-400 text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Please read this carefully before using any information from Txchyon
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
          {/* RED WARNING BOX */}
          <div class="mb-10 p-6 bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/20 rounded-xl border-2 border-red-200 dark:border-red-800">
