                  <strong>Txchyon provides educational content only.</strong> We are NOT financial advisors, 
                  brokers, or registered investment advisors. Nothing on this Site constitutes financial advice.
                </p>
                <p class="text-red-700 dark:text-red-300">
                  Crypto investments can result in <strong>COMPLETE LOSS OF FUNDS.</strong> Never invest more than you can afford to lose.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          {/* AFFILIATE DISCLOSURE - NEW SECTION */}
          <section class="mb-10 p-6 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 rounded-xl border border-blue-100 dark:border-blue-800">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="text-3xl text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">üí∞</div>
              <div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-300 mb-3">
                  Affiliate Links Disclosure
                </h2>
