                  <strong>We use affiliate links to keep this site running.</strong> When you click on links to 
                  exchanges, wallets, or tools we recommend, we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.
                </p>
                <p class="text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-300 mb-4">
                  This helps us:
                </p>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-300">
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <span class="text-blue-500 mt-1">‚Ä¢</span>
                    <span>Keep all educational content 100% free (no paywalls)</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <span class="text-blue-500 mt-1">‚Ä¢</span>
                    <span>Cover hosting and development costs</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <span class="text-blue-500 mt-1">‚Ä¢</span>
                    <span>Create more high-quality guides</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
