                  Affiliate commissions never influence our recommendations‚Äîwe prioritize your education and safety first.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold dark:text-white text-gray-900 mb-4">1. No Investment Recommendations</h2>
            <p class="dark:text-gray-300 text-gray-700 mb-4">
              We do NOT:
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 dark:text-gray-300 text-gray-700">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-red-500 mt-1">‚úó</span>
                <span>Recommend specific cryptocurrencies to buy or sell</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-red-500 mt-1">‚úó</span>
                <span>Provide price predictions or trading signals</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-red-500 mt-1">‚úó</span>
                <span>Tell you when to enter or exit positions</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-red-500 mt-1">‚úó</span>
                <span>Guarantee profits or specific returns</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold dark:text-white text-gray-900 mb-4">2. Crypto Risks You Must Understand</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div class="p-5 bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/10 rounded-xl border border-red-100 dark:border-red-800">
                <h4 class="font-bold text-red-700 dark:text-red-400 mb-2">Market Risks</h4>
                <ul class="text-sm space-y-1 text-red-600 dark:text-red-300">
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Extreme price volatility</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ 24/7 market operations</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Low liquidity in some assets</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Market manipulation risks</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="p-5 bg-orange-50 dark:bg-orange-900/10 rounded-xl border border-orange-100 dark:border-orange-800">
                <h4 class="font-bold text-orange-700 dark:text-orange-400 mb-2">Technical Risks</h4>
                <ul class="text-sm space-y-1 text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-300">
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Smart contract vulnerabilities</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Protocol hacks and exploits</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Wallet security failures</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Exchange insolvency</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="p-5 bg-purple-50 dark:bg-purple-900/10 rounded-xl border border-purple-100 dark:border-purple-800">
                <h4 class="font-bold text-purple-700 dark:text-purple-400 mb-2">Regulatory Risks</h4>
                <ul class="text-sm space-y-1 text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-300">
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Changing regulations</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Tax implications</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Geographic restrictions</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Legal uncertainty</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="p-5 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/10 rounded-xl border border-blue-100 dark:border-blue-800">
                <h4 class="font-bold text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400 mb-2">Operational Risks</h4>
                <ul class="text-sm space-y-1 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-300">
                  <li>‚Ä¢ User error (wrong addresses)</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Phishing and scams</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Lost private keys</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Rug pulls and exit scams</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold dark:text-white text-gray-900 mb-4">3. Your Responsibility</h2>
            <div class="p-6 bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20 rounded-xl border border-green-100 dark:border-green-800">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-700 dark:text-green-400 mb-4">Always Do Your Own Research (DYOR)</h3>
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 text-xl">üîç</span>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold dark:text-white text-gray-900">Verify Information</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm dark:text-gray-300 text-gray-700">
                      Cross-check our content with multiple sources. Don't trust, verify.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 text-xl">üìä</span>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold dark:text-white text-gray-900">Understand Projects</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm dark:text-gray-300 text-gray-700">
                      Read whitepapers, check team credentials, audit reports.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 text-xl">‚öñÔ∏è</span>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold dark:text-white text-gray-900">Know Your Limits</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm dark:text-gray-300 text-gray-700">
                      Only invest what you can afford to lose completely.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 text-xl">üîê</span>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold dark:text-white text-gray-900">Secure Your Assets</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm dark:text-gray-300 text-gray-700">
                      Use hardware wallets, enable 2FA, never share private keys.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold dark:text-white text-gray-900 mb-4">4. Past Performance ‚â† Future Results</h2>
            <p class="dark:text-gray-300 text-gray-700 mb-4">
              Historical data, backtests, and case studies are for educational purposes only.
              Crypto markets are unpredictable and past success does not guarantee future returns.
            </p>
            <div class="p-4 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg">
              <p class="text-sm italic dark:text-gray-400 text-gray-600">
                "The most dangerous words in investing are: 'This time it's different.'" - Sir John Templeton
              </p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold dark:text-white text-gray-900 mb-4">5. Testnet & Practice First</h2>
            <p class="dark:text-gray-300 text-gray-700 mb-4">
              Before using real funds with any strategy discussed here:
            </p>
            <ol class="space-y-3 dark:text-gray-300 text-gray-700 list-decimal pl-5">
              <li>Use testnets to practice</li>
              <li>Start with very small amounts</li>
              <li>Understand gas fees and transaction costs</li>
              <li>Test withdrawal processes</li>
              <li>Keep detailed records for taxes</li>
            </ol>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold dark:text-white text-gray-900 mb-4">6. Content Accuracy</h2>
            <p class="dark:text-gray-300 text-gray-700 mb-4">
              While we strive for accuracy:
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 dark:text-gray-300 text-gray-700">
              <li>Crypto moves fast - information may become outdated quickly</li>
              <li>We cannot guarantee all information is current or accurate</li>
              <li>Protocols change, vulnerabilities are discovered</li>
              <li>Always check official project documentation</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold dark:text-white text-gray-900 mb-4">7. No Professional Relationship</h2>
