              Using our Site does not create a client-advisor relationship. We are educators, not your personal
              financial advisors. For personalized advice, consult a qualified financial professional who understands
              cryptocurrency and your specific situation.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-10 p-6 bg-yellow-50 dark:bg-yellow-900/20 rounded-xl border border-yellow-100 dark:border-yellow-800">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold dark:text-white text-gray-900 mb-4">Acknowledgment</h2>
            <p class="dark:text-gray-300 text-gray-700 mb-4">
              By continuing to use Txchyon.com, you acknowledge that:
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg">
                <input type="checkbox" checked disabled class="mt-1 text-blue-600">
                <span class="dark:text-gray-300 text-gray-700">I understand this is educational content only</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg">
                <input type="checkbox" checked disabled class="mt-1 text-blue-600">
                <span class="dark:text-gray-300 text-gray-700">I accept full responsibility for my investment decisions</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg">
                <input type="checkbox" checked disabled class="mt-1 text-blue-600">
                <span class="dark:text-gray-300 text-gray-700">I understand crypto involves significant risk of loss</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg">
                <input type="checkbox" checked disabled class="mt-1 text-blue-600">
                <span class="dark:text-gray-300 text-gray-700">I will conduct my own research before investing</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg">
                <input type="checkbox" checked disabled class="mt-1 text-blue-600">
                <span class="dark:text-gray-300 text-gray-700">I understand affiliate links help keep this site free</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <div class="text-center pt-6 border-t dark:border-gray-700 border-gray-200">
            <p class="dark:text-gray-400 text-gray-600 text-sm">
              Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { month: 'long', day: 'numeric', year: 'numeric' })}<br>
              This disclaimer supplements our <a href="/terms" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">Terms of Service</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>